// Update or create a TimeTable
const timeTable = await prisma.timeTable.upsert({
  create: {
    // ... data to create a TimeTable
  },
  update: {
    // ... in case it already exists, update
  },
  where: {
    // ... the filter for the TimeTable we want to update
  }
})

Input

Name Type Required
where TimeTableWhereUniqueInput Yes
create TimeTableCreateInput | TimeTableUncheckedCreateInput Yes
update TimeTableUpdateInput | TimeTableUncheckedUpdateInput Yes

Output

Type: TimeTable
Required: Yes
List: No
